{"tid":319900,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"老娘的草根飯堂 - 慢煮茶滷牛腱","createTime":"2017-07-13T06:43:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-17T02:18:53.000Z","uid":30742,"like":24,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b94514a39ce9c9854e57d3f322fc82436f9ce5d5","tid":319900,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T06:43:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/FxDgb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FFxDgb.jpg&h=123794b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">＊＊＊我唔記得揀飲食台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ＊＊＊</span></strong><br />\n我呢排真係慢煮煮上癮  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n實在太方便喇！  <br />\n星期六整好入水，星期日拎出黎做finishing就得！  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中間可以做下其他野！<br />\n今次試下做滷水，一般既滷水野其實就咁煮已經好方便！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係牛展成日都會好柴或者好韌   <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用慢煮就岩晒啦！<br />\n第一次我試4個鐘，都係韌  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後再試15個鐘就差唔多了！<br />\n係淋既但又唔係入口即化，仲有少少趙口！   <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/5NGV9Rmg3gE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fy