/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後再試15個鐘就差唔多了！<br />\n係淋既但又唔係入口即化，仲有少少趙口！   <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/5NGV9Rmg3gE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F5NGV9Rmg3gE&d=4CUHfHfhw73k%2BU7XXPaFJUkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=88a17cc1\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/5NGV9Rmg3gE</a><br />\n<br />\n食譜:<br />\n慢煮茶滷牛腱: <br />\n<a href=\"http://oldlady0914.blogspot.hk/2017/07/sous-vide-marinated-beef-shank-shin.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Foldlady0914.blogspot.hk%2F2017%2F07%2Fsous-vide-marinated-beef-shank-shin.html&d=4CUHfHfhw73k%2BU7XXPaFJUkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=609ff1c4\" target=\"_blank\">http://oldlady0914.blogspot.hk/2017/07/sous-vide-marinated-beef-shank-shin.html</a><br />\nFacebook : <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/oldladycanteen/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Foldladycanteen%2F&d=4CUHfHfhw73k%2BU7XXPaFJUkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=bc5e632c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/oldladycanteen/</a><br />\nInstagram: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/_oldlady_/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2F_oldlady_%2F&d=4CUHfHfhw73k%2BU7XXPaFJUkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=3f99995b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/_oldlady_/</a><br />\nBlog: <a href=\"http://oldlady0914.blogspot.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Foldlady0914.blogspot.hk%2F&d=4CUHfHfhw73k%2BU7XXPaFJUkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=c9262c6d\" target=\"_blank\">http://oldlady0914.blogspot.hk/</a></blockquote><br />\n用焗都得</blockquote><br />\n點整？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n焗爐較110度焗三個半鐘勁淋，我成都咁整牛腱牛跟</blockquote><br />\n洗唔洗加水焗？</blockquote><br />\n一定要我放洋蔥甘筍睇底，用滷水未試過我諗一樣得</blockquote><br />\n我怕一切會散開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同埋柴...<br />\n<br />\n慢煮好處係保持到個嫩度<br />\n不過我真係要戒一戒！太著迷了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7836e7d706ff1e6c2877aa36520af6c96cb92c89","tid":319900,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T15:40:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>,,,</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5df6daba4059bc01ee64705782fb6a6c3eb0c16d","tid":319900,"uid":67432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T16:13:20.000Z","msg":"屋企無位擺只能羨慕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85707d8322452225097ae9f7a8bc5c70303a78a2","tid":319900,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T18:02:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4c4887e78c48603322442029abeabb20bd82d7f","tid":319900,"uid":350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T18:36:50.000Z","msg":"慢煮機會唔會好曬電 你咁樣開勁耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"371a2d7fc5846ffabff9c22a9eaec2218ed080f7","tid":319900,"uid":17319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T18:54:45.000Z","msg":"屌 入錯post 好餓<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7affc7f17d758678082454c6173d895035db4e00","tid":319900,"uid":75525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T19:05:31.000Z","msg":"請教開住火 15小時 會唔會好貴 煤氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0239a81e3c93ede088a8270143df0194ce8f8bcf","tid":319900,"uid":14091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T21:51:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>請教開住火 15小時 會唔會好貴 煤氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係支棍加熱架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57bb01aa959ab3b8306ae66cda2607b64cbc54c1","tid":319900,"uid":39948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T23:13:20.000Z","msg":"係咪即係牛𦟌？香港好少人叫牛腱"},{"pid":"0b9e3b9af52a3f643249d4b6b0cfde8635857a35","tid":319900,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T02:07:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>慢煮機會唔會好曬電 你咁樣開勁耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔會架～有人做過實驗<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://sousvide.smartno1.com/sv-power-consumption\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsousvide.smartno1.com%2Fsv-power-consumption&d=4CUHfHfhw73k%2BU7XXPaFJUkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=665c59ab\" target=\"_blank\">http://sousvide.smartno1.com/sv-power-consumption</a>"},{"pid":"078e927a845d28467698d63e2f6b49ff5a71381d","tid":319900,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T02:07:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>請教開住火 15小時 會唔會好貴 煤氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n用電的～放心～唔會好貴～<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"702f367ee4896129c50c0037b846919d1d2c8afb","tid":319900,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T02:08:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪即係牛𦟌？香港好少人叫牛腱</blockquote><br />\n係呀！我搵唔到個𦟌字～～<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"730e0260fab19c37509fd8375a045ffcdeb344c9","tid":319900,"uid":126046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T06:00:49.000Z","msg":"支持老娘<br />\n<br />\n緊係覺得慢煮啲野食唔夠熟"},{"pid":"c0a164080ba55249a263db6b966a87b255b05300","tid":319900,"uid":30742,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T08:45:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>支持老娘<br />\n<br />\n緊係覺得慢煮啲野食唔夠熟</blockquote><br />\n慢煮唔熟係錯覺黎～<br />\n  當肌肉受熱後，蛋白質變化令細胞變得不透明，海鮮的細胞對熱力較敏感，在較低溫（攝氏四十度）開始變色，肉類的肌紅蛋白於攝氏六十開始釋放氧氣，肌紅蛋白於缺氧情況下變得深色，肉塊變成不透明啡白色。若於此時停止加熱，過了數分鐘，肌紅蛋白接觸空氣後會變成粉紅或紅色。故此低溫慢煮的肉類多數呈粉紅色。<br />\n<br />\n        若肉塊的溫度過了攝氏六十度，肌紅蛋白會永久轉化成啡白色。繼續加熱，烹煮溫度達攝氏一百七十度，「梅納反應」令肉的表面呈金黃色或深啡色。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.stheadline.com/dailynews/headline_news_detail_columnist.asp?id=375814&amp;section_name=wtt&amp;kw=-1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.stheadline.com%2Fdailynews%2Fheadline_news_detail_columnist.asp%3Fid%3D375814%26section_name%3Dwtt%26kw%3D-1&d=4CUHfHfhw73k%2BU7XXPaFJUkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=a93dd0af\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.stheadline.com%2Fdailynews%2Fheadline_news_detail_columnist.asp%3Fid%3D375814%26section_name%3Dwtt%26kw%3D-1&h=226a4e1e\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.stheadline.com/dailynews/headline_news_detail_columnist.asp?id=375814&amp;section_name=wtt&amp;kw=-1</a>"},{"pid":"b081a001ad9e65c2d6d28417ee769b1e880b98c7","tid":319900,"uid":34427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"